  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 6th Level, when you cast a Genjutsu while your target is under the effects of Sensing Technique, they cannot gain advantage on the save in anyway.</p><p> Additionally, if a creature would succeed on a saving throw against your Genjutsu while your target is under the effects of Sensing Technique, you can force them to roll again, at disadvantage.</p><p> Once you use Chakra Distortion in this way you cannot do so again until you finish a long rest.</p><p></p>",
